  <entry>
    <title>第n杯还是很好喝</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2021/08/04/%E5%B0%8F%E8%83%96/drink/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/2021/08/04/%E5%B0%8F%E8%83%96/drink/</id>
    <published>2021-08-04T12:23:41.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-08-05T08:47:54.093Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><p>小胖说今天星巴克买一送一<br><img                       lazyload                     src="/images/loading.svg"                     data-src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Xcloud1988/Pix@master/images/drink1.aedjit2e33k.jpg"                                     ></p><p>味道还不错，今天我也发现了羊毛，和小胖一起在踩雷的边缘勇敢前进。<br><img                       lazyload                     src="/images/loading.svg"                     data-src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Xcloud1988/Pix@master/images/drink2.6c8xolgs0b00.jpg"                                     ></p><p>小胖的，哎嘿，就没有我拍的好看<br><img                       lazyload                     src="/images/loading.svg"                     data-src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Xcloud1988/Pix@master/images/drink8.5b97k57ziuc0.jpg"                                     ></p><p>台风来了！台风来了！冒着生命不可承受之风去拿Tims。嗯么，口感还是不错的，这波血赚。<br>喝太快，没拍。这是来自另一天的Tims和可颂。<br><img                       lazyload                     src="/images/loading.svg"                     data-src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Xcloud1988/Pix@master/images/drink4.64kclxm2beo0.jpg"                                     ></p><p>今天喝奶茶，被小胖忽悠扔掉盖子，头顶凉凉<br><img                       lazyload                     src="/images/loading.svg"                     data-src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Xcloud1988/Pix@master/images/drink7.6af5tjtwhx40.jpg"                                     ></p><p>终于还是踩雷了，把这段时间来的第一次交给了瑞幸。杨梅，甜到牙疼，食之头疼，弃之可惜。<br>噢噢噢，还有我的airpods小皮肤。<br><img                       lazyload                     src="/images/loading.svg"                     data-src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Xcloud1988/Pix@master/images/drink3.2021t34o9vs0.jpg"                                     ></p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
